The Beauty of LaTeX: Using TeX with expert fonts
_____________________________________

This repo hosts materials used in my 2008 article, showcasing how to use XeTeX with advanced features of OpenType fonts and comparing overall typographical quality between TeX and word processors.
All contents are released under a CC-BY-SA 3.0 license
http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/

--
Dario Taraborelli (2008) The Beauty of LaTeX, http://nitens.org/taraborelli/latex
